body.description: Enhance your home’s scent with Air Wick Scented Oil Refills infused with 100% natural essential oils. Air Wick Scented Oil Refills release continuous fragrance for up to 60 days (based on low setting) so your home smells welcoming. Our latest Air Wick scented oil warmer optimizes airflow for 360 degree fragrance diffusion, reaching every corner of the room for a consistent fragrance experience. The Air Wick Scented Oil warmer also allows you to choose between 5 fragrance settings for just the right amount of fragrance. It continuously diffuses and carefully blends fragrance throughout your home, office, or any space.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 14, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Switching to Air Wick Plug Ins from B&BW wallflowers was key in keeping my house smell as cozy and fragranced as I can get it. Other brands scents wear off extremely fast and the refills cost more. Not only are the plug ins more affordable, the scents last sooo much longer. I can get 4-5 week of STRONG ACTIVE fragrance from them, whereas with others, the bold scent is much less noticeable after a week or so. The package does say up to 300 days of scent, but that must be on the lower settings. I typically keep my plug ins fully open (on setting 5), but with this scent I've been able to lower it to 3 or 4 because this scent is so strongly fragranced, in a good way. I've tried multiple scents (fresh scents, musky scents, ocean/water scents, and nature scents - (excluding pine/trees) are my go-to's) and this is exactly what I was looking for. It smells like a fresh dewey morning in a bamboo garden, I love this being the signature scent for my home, everyone compliments how good my house smells. Nothing more relaxing than coming home to a house that smells good, Air Wick itself and this scent in particular and are forever my home scent staple items!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Spa like scent
reviews.reviewText: I just received and plugged these in. Perfect! I am VERY particular when it comes to scent since I can get headaches from scents. Unless I can smell these items in a store I tend to stick with what I’ve used in the past. Anything floral is a no go so the name of this scent was a risk. After reading reviews I decided to try it. So glad I did. Things I like:- The scent is not overwhelming but fills the room with a spa-like scent - clean (not in a linen or detergent way) and refreshing.- scent can be used year around if you want. Spring, summer, fall or winter since it’s just clean smelling.- you can smell it. I’ve used other brands and noticed the “throw” of the scent is limited and I’d need several plugins in a room. Plus it seemed the others did not last long. For whatever reason those brands work great in my dad's assisted living apartment but in my house I could only smell it when close to the plug-in. Since I just received these I don’t know if this scent will last 60 days, but based on how well they’re working in this short time I have hope.I highly recommend. Give it a shot. I’m ordering more!!!
